Ridge regression

RR \(\hat{\beta}\) , OLS , MSE.

Ridge regression \[ \sum_{i=1}^n (y_i-\hat{y}_i)^2+\lambda \sum_{j=1}^k \hat{\beta}_j^2 \]

\(\lambda\) \(\hat{\beta}_j\).

: \[ \hat{\beta}_{RR}=(X'X+\lambda I)^{-1}X'y$ \]

RR : RSS \(\sum_{j=1}^k \hat{\beta}_j^2 \leq c\). RR .

RR R :)
